videos.description: North Carolina's Joel Berry II hits back-to-back 3-pointers to help the Tar Heels' offense against the Hokies.
videos.headline: Joel Berry hits back-to-back 3-pointers

videos.description: North Carolina's Theo Pinson gets the offensive rebound and lays it in for the basket, and Joel Berry II blocks Virginia Tech's Justin Robinson on the ensuing possession.
videos.headline: UNC follows bucket by blocking VT

videos.description: North Carolina's Joel Berry II hits a three-pointer off of good ball movement to increase the Tar Heels' lead.
videos.headline: UNC's good ball movement leads to a 3-pointer

videos.description: North Carolina's Joel Berry II's great pass to Kennedy Meeks leads to an easy basket for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Berry's great pass leads to an easy bucket

videos.description: North Carolina's Justin Jackson makes the jumping  pass to Isaiah Hicks, who sinks the bucket and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Jackson's leaping pass finds Hicks for the bucket and the foul

videos.description: North Carolina's Kennedy Meeks throws down a wide-open dunk to pad the Tar Heels' lead.
videos.headline: Meeks slams down two-handed jam in win

videos.description: North Carolina's Justin Jackson nails the three-pointer from deep as the shot clock expires for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Jackson hits a deep 3 as the shot clock expires

videos.description: Breaking down North Carolina's Justin Jackson scoring against Virginia Tech.
videos.headline: Breaking Down Jackson's game against the Hokies
